## Quick Reference — Docker Commands

```bash
# Normal start (cloud provider, no Ollama)
docker compose up

# Start with file-sync hot reload (after watch is configured)
docker compose watch

# Rebuild images after code changes
docker compose up --build

# Stop everything (data preserved)
docker compose down

# Stop everything and wipe database
docker compose down -v

# View live logs
docker logs ai-librarian-backend-1 -f

# Check what's running
docker ps

# Connect to Postgres directly
docker compose exec postgres psql -U aijah -d aijah
```

